Job Details
The company is professional typing and clearing center providing Government Services to corporate companies. Reporting to the Office Manager, the Public Relations Officer will be responsible to provide services to the customers related to visa applications, medical, emirates id and other company related services.
Requirements
Applicants must be able to talk, read and write Arabic and are willing to attend to customers with strict deadlines. Send your CV to viseorecruitment@gmail.com
